  <name>FastHud</name>
  <summary>Quick MangoHud Configuration</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Easily configure MangoHud with pre-defined settings while having the option to adjust layouts between vertical and horizontal orientations. Additionally, the app automatically creates a backup of the previous MangoHud.conf file upon clicking the 'Apply' button.</p>
  </description>
